\]
Cross-multiplying:
\[
300(8R + 63) = 151 \times 15 \times (R + 9)
\]
Simplify by dividing both sides by 15:
\[
20(8R + 63) = 151(R + 9)
\]
Expand:
\[
160R + 1260 = 151R + 1359
\]
Rearrange terms:
\[
160R - 151R = 1359 - 1260
\]
\[
9R = 99
\]
Solve for \( R \):
